<ce:para>This short note presents an alternate approximation of concave cost functions used to reflect economies of scale in process design and supply chain optimization problems. To approximate the original concave function, we propose a logarithmic function that is exact and has bounded gradients at zero values in contrast to other approximation schemes. We illustrate the application and advantages of the proposed approximation. Â© 2013 Elsevier Ltd.</ce:para>
